    <div class="sun-scrolling-bg sun-bg-3 section">
      <div class="row sun-promo-content">
        <div class="large-12 columns text-center">
          <h2>Huge purpose</h2>
          <h3>We might destroy the planet if you don't.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sun-scrolling-bg sun-bg-5 section">
      <div class="row sun-promo-content">
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <h3 class="highlight-2 uppercase">Tens of billions of dollars and more than 40 years have been invested to get solar where it is today.</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <p class="uppercase"><b>a mainstream, economically viable alternative to dirty fossil fuels.</b></p>
          <p>The race is now on to grab the rooftop real estate, and that’s why we need YOU.  You now hold the key to getting the word out about solar, and helping us to turn the tide from dirty energy to CLEAN renewables all in the next decade.</p>
          <p>We believe solar is not only one of the greatest financial opportunities you might see in a lifetime, but also an incredible opportunity to shift the scales of power on planet earth for the betterment of us all.  For the last 150 years, a very small group of companies has controlled the “power”, meaning the energy markets, almost exclusively.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sun-scrolling-bg sun-bg-13 section inverted">
      <div class="row sun-promo-content">
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <h2><span class="highlight-2">Solar</span> <br />represents the decentralization of that power.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <p>Instead of the wealth of energy only flowing to oil or coal companies… the wealth from the energy industry can now flow through the hands of people just like you.  By sharing solar person to person, we return power back to the people both financially (by getting paid), and literally, by powering our homes from our own rooftops.  This is “power to the people” in its truest sense.</p>
          <p>The time has never been better to join the cause, and live a meaningful, rewarding life… while building a high income business making a difference.  Your great grand-children will thank you one day for taking your stand, and the wealth they may inherit!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sun-scrolling-bg sun-bg-3 section">
